  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to examine the effect of levodopa-carbidopa intestinal
      gel (LCIG) compared with optimized medical treatment (OMT) on dyskinesia in participants with
      advanced Parkinson's disease (PD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
